data.description: Looking to spread out a bit?   This beautiful home sits on a 3/4 acre lot on Harlingen's north side.  A really unique floor plan with a courtyard in the middle.  Four bedrooms and three baths plus an upstairs bonus room/office. The kitchen has dark cabinets with built-in microwave and oven, electric cooktop and a beautiful island with sink overlooking the living room.   You'll love the stone accent wall in the living room and all tile flooring.  Huge laundry room with sink and cabinetry.  Side entry two car garage and the entire yard has a privacy fence, although some of the fence needs to be repaired.     The master suite is well appointed with large walk-in closet, jetted tub, oversized shower and a couple vanity.  Plenty of room for a pool, shop/barn etc here!  This home is being sold in its present condition - no repairs will be made.  Water and electric are on for inspections.
